STATE
v.
Henry Earl HARRIS. No. 261P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 27, 2007. LaToya B. Powell, Assistant Attorney General, C. Branson Vickory, III, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 5th day of June 2007 by Defendant for "Petition for Writ of Certiorari":
